Title: Slave Nurses [DVD]

reviewText: A strange epidemic is running rampant in a local hospital. Every night the nurses are having an uncontrollable urge. They have to satisfy it with the doctors, patients, and with each other. The new resident doctor is starting to feel the same urges. He also has a suspicion that someone is behind this crazy activity.This is the first hentai I've owned. I have been an anime fan for a long time, and I was kinda curious to see what this was like. As far as a porno goes, this is a little better than average. It does have really good animation, and some pretty cool characters. The story is really thin, but that's just the way stuff like this is I guess. As I said before, I have never owned anything liek this before, so I don't really have a fram of reference. I don't think I'll spend my money on stuff this over the top in the future. I do think that if you are into hentai that this will probably be a good choice for you though. If you are looking for guilty pleasures and lots of fun, Slave Nurses has both.
Title: Slave Nurses [DVD]

reviewText: A little on the sadistic side, garnished with scat. Nurses taken avantage of by a physican who is determined to dominate and a little nuts.  Passsable art work, conspiracies galore. The new Doc is driven by contrasting urges of good and evil and his job is to 'break-in' the nurses who will be the attracants to the rich suckers. One female lead out-evils all the rest of the antagonists but even she succumbs to . . . . .
